                  high level design discussions in order to provide insightful
                  ideas and lanes of thoughts for solving problems with
                  software.
                </li>
                <li>
                  Contributed to an agile development process from sprint
                  planning to retrospective by communicating road blocks and
                  collaborating with other developers to achieve current sprint
                  goals on a biweekly sprint schedule.
