              <p>09/2021-12/2021</p>
              <p>Ottawa, Ontario</p>
            </span>
            <div class="work-details">
              <ul>
                <li>
                  Worked closely with other developers, the Product Owner and UX
                  to improve product usability by developing new features to
                  their microservice architecture web application using mainly
                  <b>Django</b> and <b>Angular</b>.
                </li>
                <li>
                  Maintained customer satisfaction by reproducing and resolving
                  bugs in a timely manner.
                </li>
                <li>
                  Participated in Agile development process through <b>SCRUM</b>
                  activities such as sprint planning, stand-ups and
                  retrospective meetings
                </li>
              </ul>
            </div>
          </div>

          <div class="section-content">
            <h3>Information Technoly Analyst</h3>
            <h4>National Research Council of Canada</h4>
            <span class="time">
              <p>05/2020-08/2020 & 01/2021-04/2021</p>
              <p>Ottawa, Ontario</p>
            </span>
            <div class="work-details">
              <ul>
                <li>
                  Expanded on my knowledge of automation applications by working
                  with <b>MS Power Apps</b> and Power Virtual Agent.
                </li>
                <li>
                  Developed a comprehensive project plan to implement a
                  Microsoft Bot Framework based Chatbot in a timely matter
                </li>
                <li>
                  Documented project functionalities, gathered constraints and
                  requirements for maintenance and quality assurance purposes.
                </li>
                <li>
                  Developed complementary features with a server scripting
                  language in <b>PHP</b> for an IT request management web
                  application.
                </li>
                <li>
                  Implemented new database management reports using
                  <b>ORACLE DB</b>
                  queries and a Microsoft task automation language called
                  <b>PowerShell</b>.
                </li>
                <li>
                  Facilitated the adoption and use of MS Teams across
                  NRC-Construction by providing a documentation for FAQ in the
                  form of a Wiki in MS Teams.
                </li>
              </ul>
            </div>
          </div>
        </section>
      </main>
    </div>
<style>

@import url("https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Open+Sans:wght@300;400;500;600;700&display=swap");

:root {
  --accent: #34678c;
  --accent-lg: #99b3c5;
}
* {
  padding: 0;
  margin: 0;
  box-sizing: border-box;
  font-family: "Open Sans", "sans-serif";
}

a,
a:hover {
  text-decoration: none;
  color: black;
}
li {
  list-style-type: square;
}
header {
  width: 99%;
  margin: 1em 0 2em 1em;
  height: 20%;
  background-color: var(--accent);
  color: white;
  float: right;
  padding: 1em;
}
header span {
  display: block;
  width: 15em;
  height: 1.5em;
  border-bottom: 1px solid white;
  margin-bottom: 0.4em;
}

.main-container {
  width: 100%;
  height: 100%;
  display: flex;
  justify-content: space-around;
}
aside {
  width: 20%;
  height: fit-content;
  display: flex;
  flex-direction: column;
  gap: 2em;
}
main {
  width: 70%;
  height: 100%;
}
.contacts {
  width: 100%;
  height: 25%;
  display: flex;
  flex-direction: column;
  gap: 1em;
}
.media {
  display: flex;
  flex-wrap: wrap;
  gap: 0.3em;
}
.skills {
  width: 100%;
  height: 25%;
  display: flex;
  flex-direction: column;
}
.langs {
  width: 100%;
  height: 25%;
  display: flex;
  flex-direction: column;
}
.interests {
  width: 100%;
  height: 25%;
  display: flex;
  flex-direction: column;
}

.heading {
  display: block;
  width: 100%;
  height: 2em;
  border-bottom: 2px solid var(--accent);
  margin-bottom: 0.4em;
}
.heading h2,
.section-content h3 {
  color: var(--accent);
}
.section-content {
  margin: 1em 0;
}

.time {
  width: 100%;
  display: flex;
  justify-content: space-between;
  color: var(--accent-lg);
  margin-bottom: 0.5em;
}
.education {
  width: 100%;
  height: 20%;
}

.work {
  width: 100%;
  height: 100%;
}

.sk-container {
  width: 100%;
  height: fit-content;
  display: flex;
  gap: 0.2em;
  flex-wrap: wrap;
}
.sk {
  width: fit-content;
  height: fit-content;
  padding: 0.5em;
  background-color: var(--accent-lg);
  color: white;
  border-radius: 10px;
}

i {
  color: var(--accent);
}
.lang {
  margin: 1em 0;
}
.inter-container {
  width: 100%;
  height: fit-content;
  display: flex;
  flex-wrap: wrap;
  gap: 1em;
}
.inter {
  width: fit-content;
  height: fit-content;
  padding: 0.5em;
  border: 1px solid black;

  border-radius: 5px;
}

</style>
